selection occurred in coexisting clones, and its function might be too weak or 
too time-limited to make the clonal exclusion occur. Genetic drift might play an 
important role in genotype frequency variation. The coexistence of different 
genotype clones of B. calyciflorus population is of significance for the 
existence of the population in water environment.

