Defining the importance of phosphatidylserine synthase-1 (PSS1): unexpected 
viability of PSS1-deficient mice.

Arikketh D(1), Nelson R, Vance JE.

Author information:
(1)University of Alberta, Edmonton, Alberta T6G 2S2, Canada.

